=head1 NAME

Dist::Banshee - A lightweight authoring tool

=head1 VERSION

0.001

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Dist::Banshee is a lightweight authoring tool. It intends to be (largely) reproducible build, using scripts that are part of your repository.

=head1 SEE ALSO

=over 4

=item * L<Dist::Zilla|Dist::Zilla>

A maximum-overkill extensible framework for building distributions.

=item * L<App::ModuleBuildTiny|App::ModuleBuildTiny>

An even more minimalist authoring tool. Functional but not extensible.

=back

